{"tid":1442763,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"就係有班人一路講要智取","createTime":"2019-08-11T04:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:47:54.000Z","uid":23630,"like":50,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"70b5ac8156d1671318e3f8103831943f4d4edf1c","tid":1442763,"uid":23630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:57:12.000Z","msg":"香港就係香港，就係有班人一路講要智取，周身潔癖，其實就一個大字講撚哂，怕事，淆底，無撚腦。<br />\n<br />\n爆玻璃係咁，掉磚係咁，和你飛又係咁。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 係呢班人眼中勇武就係無撚腦，鳩衝<br />\n你地就係最撚冷靜，最好乜撚都唔想付出就可以有成果<br />\n<br />\n請繼續用呢種態度做人，你一世都將會係咁 <br />\n成班廢人"},{"pid":"1fc3b3599ab45229de15b512fd1ab88c38bceba2","tid":1442763,"uid":23630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:57:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bb61c49c3c905b1b66c32badf4a6fbc82b41819f","tid":1442763,"uid":23630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bca982ff9a11986ba68b41477d4da208e2ac20f4","tid":1442763,"uid":23630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eeafb9ce854efba6b2616cddc5cb470103bbfc7f","tid":1442763,"uid":23630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:57:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d981fb0c9b75762fe520008e9256d26a11e97a34","tid":1442763,"uid":23630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:59:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d9203a9355cc30ef5d3aee3e81fcaa0ab76ff57f","tid":1442763,"uid":23630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:01:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8c4f2e172aadfe71ceb93506450257972c07ac46","tid":1442763,"uid":23630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:02:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e024bcb9a16ea85a68fb7810f7e5aa44fd77c344","tid":1442763,"uid":23630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:07:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ac3f686981ade7d0686978938c2492838eb3b0c3","tid":144